  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join our Discord Server</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/d8996ddd06d9c6e6d8e9ffc2702caa5c.avif?t=1758645973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras_big/d8996ddd06d9c6e6d8e9ffc2702caa5c.avif?t=1758645973 width=800 height=196 /></span></p></p><br><h1>DEMO IS OUT NOW!</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/7f02070439b7826db8c1c8b535f0847b.avif?t=1758645973\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras_big/7f02070439b7826db8c1c8b535f0847b.avif?t=1758645973 width=800 height=1234 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/601882e2a24e06e6dd4689bac52776da.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/601882e2a24e06e6dd4689bac52776da.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/601882e2a24e06e6dd4689bac52776da.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Escape an Empire Gone Mad</strong></i><br>The Empire has fallen. Its survivors are trapped within an apocalypse of its own creation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can you assemble a band of heroes and escape the Mad Empire?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/9b8c6b697862c2de79a60d78133372b5.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/9b8c6b697862c2de79a60d78133372b5.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/9b8c6b697862c2de79a60d78133372b5.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Gather your Heroes</strong></i> <br>Master the full potential of a varied party of heroes, choosing from a pool of 13 classes. Unlock their full potential via skills, loot and more. <br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/8c44fe210c43512a7f23d0b986d6a623.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/8c44fe210c43512a7f23d0b986d6a623.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/8c44fe210c43512a7f23d0b986d6a623.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Wield Insane Loot</strong></i> <br>In its madness, the Empire used crystals to create absurd and cursed items. In Escape the Mad Empire, each piece of loot is as meaningful as it is unhinged.<br><br> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/1d2f7a9b3f234ceb0aa9a485f52ee3e1.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/1d2f7a9b3f234ceb0aa9a485f52ee3e1.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/1d2f7a9b3f234ceb0aa9a485f52ee3e1.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Strategize in the Blink of an Eye</strong></i> <br>Masterfully employ your heroes and their items in order to survive the apocalypse. Pause the action at any moment to instantly use spells, abilities and consumables, turning the tide of the battle in your favor! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/c4d08259c155eb129a47471cd0daaabf.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/c4d08259c155eb129a47471cd0daaabf.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/c4d08259c155eb129a47471cd0daaabf.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Construct Mad Machines</strong></i><br>Your hub is your sanctuary. There you can use the Crystals of Reality to build awesome machines, which allow you to recruit, upgrade or restore heroes, buy, craft, identify or enchant gear, and more. Relax as you theorycraft the ultimate party!   .</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/52acc75c9d8f0e7c435f42045ce2d178.poster.avif?t=1758645973\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/52acc75c9d8f0e7c435f42045ce2d178.webm?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1823390/extras/52acc75c9d8f0e7c435f42045ce2d178.mp4?t=1758645973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Chart Your Way Through the Apocalypse</strong></i><br>In each daring attempt at escape, you will chart your own path through the cavernous maze dug out by the Mad Empire. Take daring risks to reap big rewards, and face bosses at the end of each run. With each successful escape, your heroes are rewarded with resources used to develop your home base, and let you continue your journey through the Mad Empire’s apocalypse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you Escape the Mad Empire?</strong></p>",
